00:47:41.165 --> 00:47:43.650 align:middle line:90%
>>MORRIS: Not until Castaneda.

00:47:43.650 --> 00:47:44.450 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:47:44.450 --> 00:47:46.130 align:middle line:90%
>>MORRIS: And OK.

