But then I read The Four
Agreements, and I had a--

00:48:08.150 --> 00:48:09.650 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Wonderful book.

00:48:09.650 --> 00:48:10.760 align:middle line:90%
>>MORRIS: Yes, it is.

