period, there were--

00:48:19.550 --> 00:48:20.760 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't sell anything.

00:48:20.760 --> 00:48:21.560 align:middle line:90%
I would just send--

00:48:21.560 --> 00:48:23.630 align:middle line:84%
