I wanted to pursue that
as far as it would go.

00:49:20.073 --> 00:49:21.990 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You wanted to
expand your awareness.

00:49:21.990 --> 00:49:23.570 align:middle line:84%
You wanted to expand
your consciousness.

00:49:23.570 --> 00:49:25.445 align:middle line:84%
>>MORRIS: So I went into
apprentice programs,

