I went to--

00:49:33.990 --> 00:49:36.250 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You were a
man seeking yourself.

00:49:36.250 --> 00:49:37.050 align:middle line:90%
>>MORRIS: Yes.

00:49:37.050 --> 00:49:37.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:49:37.850 --> 00:49:40.810 align:middle line:10%
>>MORRIS: And to the
degree that I found myself,

00:49:40.810 --> 00:49:41.730 align:middle line:10%
that's where I did it.

00:49:41.730 --> 00:49:45.270 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, and you did it
at a time and in a generation

